content:
Please provide the HTML code for a basic webpage with a header, body and footer sections. Also, include a CSS style code to change the font color of the header section to red.
Data format:
You must have [ HTML page ] and [ CSS code ] data types in the following Rewrite prompt
Rewrite prompt:
Create a basic webpage with a header, body and footer sections. The header section should have a background color of blue and a font color of red. The body section should have a background color of white and contain some text. The footer section should have a background color of black and contain some text.
HTML Code:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>My Basic Webpage</title>
    <style>
      header {
        background-color: blue;
        color: red;
      }
      body {
        background-color: white;
      }
      footer {
        background-color: black;
        color: white;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Welcome to My Basic Webpage</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>This is the main content of my webpage.</p>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>Copyright © 2021 My Basic Webpage</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

